StrEdit
=======

A minimalistic STRINGS, ILSTRINGS and DLSTRINGS file editor designed for mod
translators.

Please see the HTML readme file at "StrEdit Readme.html" for more information.


Build Instructions
==================

Under construction.

Requirements:

  * CMake
    - <http://cmake.org/>
    - Tested with v2.8.9.
  * Boost C++ Libraries
    - <http://sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/boost/>
    - Download the latest 7-zipped source code.
    - Tested with v1.51.0.
  * wxWidgets
    - <http://www.wxwidgets.org/downloads/>
    - Download the latest zipped v2.9.x source code.
    - Tested with v2.9.4.
  * libstrings
    - <http://github.com/WrinklyNinja/libstrings>
    - Download the latest source code.
  * A native build system of your choice.
    - Tested with GNU Make on Ubuntu Linux 12.10.

    mkdir ../../build
    cd ../../build
    cmake .. -DSTREDIT_ARCH=32 -DSTREDIT_LINK=STATIC -DCMAKE_SYSTEM_NAME=Windows
    make
